### User API 테스트 ###

### 1. 프로필 이미지 Presigned URL 생성 (public)
POST {{baseUrl}}/user/presigned-url?access=public
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

[
  {
    "filename": "profile.jpg",
    "contentType": "image/jpeg"
  }
]

### 2. 프로필 이미지 Presigned URL 생성 (private)
POST {{baseUrl}}/user/presigned-url?access=private
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

[
  {
    "filename": "private-profile.jpg",
    "contentType": "image/jpeg"
  }
]

### 3. 사용자 정보 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/user/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 4. 사용자 정보 수정 (프로필 이미지 포함)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/user/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nickname": "새로운닉네임",
  "image": "https://your-bucket.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/public/1234567890_profile.jpg"
}

### 5. 비밀번호 변경
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/user/me/password
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "currentPassword": "현재비밀번호",
  "newPassword": "새비밀번호"
}
